Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I didn't know why we'd received our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:28.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Why we all had come into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:34.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I didn't know how to face the one beside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Only I looked away and wandered where to love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Though it was always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:46.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}If I have a tough, iron armor protecting the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I wonder if I can see you, and beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}I just want to be stronger than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:57.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}To hold you, all of, oh even the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:02.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}All the dreams end up as mere dreams, even if game's over,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I won't give up my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:06.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Even a hope may be said 'Just that's a thought'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}So I still want to reach for you hoping you live your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:12.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Only there's a truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:16.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Living for making all the moments shine with proving all times
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Just seeing your smiles, that's my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:22.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Even if we're all even in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:28.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}我们是为何而生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:34.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}爱一直就在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}我却总是视若不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}彷徨着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:46.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}如有足以保护世界的强大钢铁铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}是否能一直见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}迸发无人能及的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:57.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}去保护你的心灵 你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:02.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}如果梦想只能作为梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}即使穷途末路 我也不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:06.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}抓住零光片羽的希望光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}让你一直能做真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:16.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}我们现在和过去的一切在此绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}你的笑靥 我的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:22.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}即使在暗无天日的世界里
Comment: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================AVANT=================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,直升机停机坪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,客人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,实在招待不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是他吧 他来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要杀了我逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为不想伤害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 G2 放开她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,开枪打我然后逃走就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,它什么都不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有所觉悟 你应该能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来你只有这种程度的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我就开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜欢弄脏自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,够了吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是你输了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雷纳德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,放开那把枪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,加里宁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,带走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎只是擦伤 真乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,援军？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那也是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,被看破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,韦伯 你还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你能逃到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,通信干扰 不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,电子战也是对面占优
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会有这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有新的客人 马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人似乎也出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 捡了一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个 我比较担心宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,援军？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不 新的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？ 难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然目标女人逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但要问你的事情像山一样多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,绑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 卧倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想起了溪山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 雷蒙 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,作战失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,相良宗介 现在投下烈焰魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,烈焰… 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,烈焰魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是它自称的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这个机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.42,AI,,0,0,0,,好久不见 军曹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,AL吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.26,AI,,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:33.85,AI,,0,0,0,,但本机的名称是ARX-8 烈焰魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:38.82,AI,,0,0,0,,相良军曹 请允许我回归你的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然 我允许
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.63,AI,,0,0,0,,很光荣 首先请搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:55.15,AI,,0,0,0,,警告 敌AS巨兽3台 地狱君王3台接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.64,AI,,0,0,0,,要先大闹一场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:05.04,AI,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这个力量是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:26.05,AI,,0,0,0,,失礼了 这台机体没有试运行过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那么能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.34,AI,,0,0,0,,λ-Driver吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.66,AI,,0,0,0,,不知道 因为没用过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢 试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.00,AI,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.00,AI,,0,0,0,,成功 看来能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.26,AI,,0,0,0,,接近警报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.08,AI,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.22,AI,,0,0,0,,保持这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,辅助臂？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.86,AI,,0,0,0,,由我来控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:40.63,AI,,0,0,0,,现在的负荷推定1500吨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.25,AI,,0,0,0,,请马上逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没有其他武器了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:07.92,AI,,0,0,0,,请用这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,爆破炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,165mm？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.35,AI,,0,0,0,,威力和后坐力都很惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:19.67,AI,,0,0,0,,没有λ-Driver无法开炮 请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,强制击发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:27.49,AI,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:36.91,AI,,0,0,0,,成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.74,AI,,0,0,0,,贯穿对方的力场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.94,AI,,0,0,0,,一台巨兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.09,AI,,0,0,0,,放弃战斗撤退中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:56.73,AI,,0,0,0,,要追击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,以这个武器的射程已经不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.93,AI,,0,0,0,,不 是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:11.43,AI,,0,0,0,,爆破炮 切换至榴弹模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.20,AI,,0,0,0,,最大射程是30km
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.92,AI,,0,0,0,,命中 击破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,脱离危险空域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好 保持这个高度 向北北西去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是认真的 现在马上掉头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你还蛮精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,掉头回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我会射这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,随你便 毕竟是自己的枪都管理不好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:12:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真开枪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就像刚才对雷纳德・泰斯特罗莎做的那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有开枪觉悟的人不能拿枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,强迫自己的意志就意味着伤害什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做到 所以现在在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 我已经没法见到他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定 把枪给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 我会尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让直升机回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那个还是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,需要为雷纳德治伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还有被敌人击坠的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那让我道别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,无线通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可是这全是宗介干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,吓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,烈焰魔剑来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好可靠的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要是当时这家伙在美利达岛上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,待会儿再告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个 相良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽量不想让俘虏看到那个机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\b0\bord0\be2\c&H535651&\frz327.1\pos(935.667,492.333)}妖精的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\fsp2\pos(915,995)}Electromagnetic Camouflage System
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,AL 发动ECS 不可视模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.76,AI,,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:13.21,AI,,0,0,0,,这台机体没有搭载ECS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.77,AI,,0,0,0,,犯规的力量 λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:20.69,AI,,0,0,0,,没有空间搭载多余的电子器材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎没有电子装备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是现代战争 你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:28.15,AI,,0,0,0,,可以和同伴进行数据连接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:31.00,AI,,0,0,0,,不要灰心加油吧 军曹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有个多余的器材哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,应该把你扔进垃圾桶 换成ECS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.54,AI,,0,0,0,,这个提议是荒谬的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.57,AI,,0,0,0,,没有我 这个机体是派不上用场的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:49.06,AI,,0,0,0,,捕捉到新的无线信号 似乎在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.56,AI,,0,0,0,,要接上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟 是千鸟吗 你在哪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里之前发生了很多 我犹豫了好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 为了救出你 带你回那个学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,住手？ 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我想寻求自由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有人会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 恭子也是 发生那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经无法忍受了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 忘掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让它结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就到此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事绝对不要 就算有人受伤也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不许动 让我说到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 我命令你 听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,无论付出什么牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,无论死多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,死几百 几万 几亿人都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以来接我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把那没有常识 给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,乱七八糟的军人技能全用上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,无论多么难缠的对手都打个落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到吧 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对会去的 等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 下次见面以后 一定要接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情的 无论在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 几亿人只是打比方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被你摆了一道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你真打算寻死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是演的 我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我有所觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你去死吧 下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,时隔半年一见面就来这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 你不是成长了很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,总之没事就好 相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有话过后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,无线通讯我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,介绍你的长官给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然一口气就过来了 但先要交涉才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,您没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾我 照顾我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙无视掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我才需要照顾！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,带走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾 照顾！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个 我来介绍他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,DGSE的特工 我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的长官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 那个 这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意给我介绍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是迷上她了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真容易理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,粉丝俱乐部喜加一吗
