Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,相良 要复归我队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是 请允许我复归本队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuatha de Danaan欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.30,AI,,0,0,0,,所谓欢迎 也包括我在内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:09.06,AI,,0,0,0,,泰斯特罗莎上校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然 AL 你没事太好了
